{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "本章围绕三条线索展开。其一，白星武与冷一枫发现赵奇刚的尸体被割去头颅，断定是铁中棠的调虎离山之计，继续追击。堡丁奉命处理尸首时偷懒，将装死的铁中棠抛入深不见底的山坑。铁中棠靠抓住山藤悬于半空，又遭遇毒蛇逼近，危在旦夕。赵奇刚在崖上悲呼，却被追杀者惨叫击杀。铁中棠最终被一条长索套住拽下深渊，失去知觉。其二，云铮在武木铁铺醒来，误以为被铁中棠出卖，对青衣少女怒喝拒绝喝药，挣扎逃出。他在路边拦截温黛黛的马车，被这位绝美妇人收留。温黛黛用迷魂丝囊将云铮迷昏，搜出大旗竹牌。其三，温黛黛回到庄院，先杀死一名被她色诱的英俊少年，再与受伤的司徒笑商议审问云铮之事。司徒笑提出美人计，温黛黛假意委屈哭泣答应，出门后却暗自得意。司徒笑识破她的伪装，但因尚未玩腻而隐忍不发。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "谁的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "赵奇刚呀赵奇刚，可怜你忠心耿耿，到死时竟尸骨不全。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "赵奇刚，可是寒枫堡里，四位教拳师傅中，武功最强的那位赵师傅？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "定必是那厮将他杀死后，割下他的头颅，换下他的衣服，想来骗过我们！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "不错，那厮最喜用这些最浅薄的计谋，而且我们已被他骗了多次！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "但这次老夫却不上他的当了，再追！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那边有人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "text": "逃了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "盛大娘",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "我这边已发现足迹，逃向林外，你们快过来，谅他身负重伤，定必逃不远的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_sheng_da_niang",
      "text": "就来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "什么足迹，只不过是她又在那里发疯罢了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "去看看亦无妨！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "speaker_name": "白星武",
      "listener": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "text": "冷兄可要留下几人，将这些尸首收拾了，免得他们曝于风露之中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "冷一枫",
      "listener": "char_bai_xing_wu",
      "text": "极是极是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "堡丁箭手甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丁老二，还不快些动手，站在那里装死么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "丁老二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "累了这大半天，我实在连脚都抬不起了，哪里还有力气挖洞埋人？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "堡丁箭手甲",
      "listener": "char_ding_lao_er",
      "text": "不埋又怎么办？堡主吩咐下来的事，你敢不办，我可没有这份胆量。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "堡丁箭手丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我倒有个法子，既省力，又不误事，不知道你们愿不愿意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "丁老二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "堡丁箭手丙",
      "listener": "char_ding_lao_er",
      "text": "离这里不远，就有一个小坑，也不知道多深，咱们把尸身往下一抛，岂非干净利落？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "丁老二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好极好极，就这么办。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁公子……铁公子，赵某来迟一步，竟见不着公子你最后一面了！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "speaker_name": "赵奇刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁公子，你在天英灵，只管放心，我已将云公子送到安全的地方了，还有人照顾着他。我完成了使命，立刻赶回，哪知……哪知却已来不及。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "追杀者",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qi_gang",
      "text": "赵奇刚，你在这里！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "你是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "滚出去！谁要吃你的脏药？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_mu",
      "speaker_name": "武木",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "他将药吃下了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_mu",
      "speaker_name": "武木",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nv",
      "text": "那少年是你义父再三交托给我们的，你必须好生看待人家，不要总是对人这样冷冷冰冰的样子，教人家看了还以为你对他有恶意哩！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年铁匠",
      "listener": "char_wu_mu",
      "text": "师傅，你老人家去歇歇不好，这几件东西又不是太难打造的暗器，你老人家何必自己动手。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_mu",
      "speaker_name": "武木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "东西虽不难打，但数量太多，寒枫堡又追得太急，我若不动手，就要误了人家寒枫堡的事。咱们跟寒枫堡来往了这么多年，可从来没有一次误过期限，这样你赵二叔也有面子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_er",
      "speaker_name": "敏儿",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你要死了么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "事态紧急，先容我上车再说，但姑娘大可放心，云某绝非歹人！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_er",
      "speaker_name": "敏儿",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "还说不是歹人，我看你不是小偷，就是强盗，再不走，小心姑娘的鞭子抽你！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "敏儿，让他上来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "夫人……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "我姓温，还不是夫人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "温姑娘请恕在下失礼，只因在下被仇家所逼，情急之下，才冒昧登车。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "没关系，我虽然手无缚鸡之力，但对江湖游侠却一向羡慕得很，何况你……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "敏儿，走慢些，云公子伤重，受不得颠震的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你怎会知道我姓云？你究竟是什么人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "公子你方才自称姓云，难道现在就忘记了么？至于我究竟是谁么……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "我只是个普通的女人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "在下伤重，仇家却甚是厉害，是以……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你不要说了，我全知道，你只管放心养伤好了，你的仇家，决不会找到我那里去的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来了！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "没关系！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？什么事？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_mu",
      "speaker_name": "武木",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "小的乃是村里打铁的武夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_wu_mu",
      "text": "你要改行做劫路的强盗么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_mu",
      "speaker_name": "武木",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "小的不敢，小的只是想请问夫人一句，有没有看到小的一个侄儿，他全身都受了重伤，神智已有些不清，不知跑到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_wu_mu",
      "text": "你侄儿失踪，也要来问我么？自己去找便是！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_er",
      "speaker_name": "敏儿",
      "listener": "char_wu_mu",
      "text": "闪开！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你仇人怎会是个铁匠？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "云铮",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "他哪里是个铁匠！只是我伤重晕迷，也不知怎会落到他手里？否则……凭他这样一个小角色，又怎能沾得着我？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你要是没有受伤，我也不会管你了。云公子，你说是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_yun_zheng",
      "text": "你好好歇着吧，到了家的时候，我自然会唤醒你的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "敏儿，快！主人不知回家了没有？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓云的，天教你落到老娘的手上，你还想逃出去么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_er",
      "speaker_name": "敏儿",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "主人今天会到这里么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "我算定他要来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_er",
      "speaker_name": "敏儿",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "那么，那个……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "我自有办法。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "英俊少年",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你回来了，我等得你好苦！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我才出去半天，你就真的这样想我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "英俊少年",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "真的，千千万万个真的。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我和你才认识三天，你就这样想我，以后怎么得了呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "英俊少年",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "以后我永远也不让你离开我了！这是上天安排的奇缘，我简直像在做梦一样，被人糊糊涂涂地就拖上了马车，糊糊涂涂地就到了这里，到了这里，到了这天堂一样的地方，遇着你这天仙一样的人。唉！那天我若不到杏花村去喝酒，怎会碰到这天降的奇缘。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "英俊少年",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "黛黛，我感激你，没有遇到你前，我真不知人生原来有这么多乐趣……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的感激我？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "英俊少年",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "黛黛，相信我……我感激得情愿为你死……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "英俊少年",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "真的，真的，黛黛，让我们……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 445
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "英俊少年",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你……你好狠……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抬他出去！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "夫人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "敏儿，你看我美吗？要不要抱一抱我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_er",
      "speaker_name": "敏儿",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "主人回来了，而且还受了伤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的？抬进来！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "将老爷放到床上，轻些！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老爷伤得重吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "抬床大汉",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "还……还好，他老人家吃……吃了白二爷一……副安神药，此刻已经睡着了。",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "傻孩子，难道一辈子没有见过女人么？来仔细看看，别偷偷摸摸的！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们看够了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "抬床大汉",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "小人……小人……",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 503,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们看到我的身子，若是被老爷知道了，哼哼！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "抬床大汉",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "小……小人们该死，请夫人饶……饶命！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去吧，我饶了你们，但以后牧场中有什么事，莫忘了来禀报于我！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男人，男人，啐！世上最不值钱的，就是男人了。我叫你们往东，你们还敢往西么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我方才到寒枫堡去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "冷一枫素来与我不睦，你难道还不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 533,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我只因为今天是你该来的日子，却听说你到寒枫堡去了，才忍不住去看看。以后再也不会去了，好么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你说得是，还有什么不好！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "听说你们去围剿大旗门人，我就担心得很，想不到你果然受了伤。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 543,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "伤势虽不重，却甚是令人气恼？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 547,
      "line_end": 547
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "为什么气恼？难道你们让大旗门人逃脱了一两个，没有全部抓到？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 549,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "非但没有全部抓到，简直连一个都未曾捉到，我竟还在阴沟里翻了船，被个少年人暗算了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "他们全逃了么？哎呀，那怎么办呢？抓到了一两个也好呀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 557,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "若有一个活着的大旗门人在我手中，自然要好得多，只可惜……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "若是有一个人，能将一个活着的大旗弟子，送到你手上，你又当怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 563,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "我即使分他一半家财，也……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 567,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "小丫头，你又有什么花样了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 569,
      "line_end": 569
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我呀，我或许抓住了一个大旗弟子！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 573,
      "line_end": 573
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 575,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "你说话算数，我说的话便是真的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 577,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你银子难道还不够花？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 579,
      "line_end": 579
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我才不要你的银子，我只要你的人！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 581,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我不要你的一半家财，我只要你将你那个讨厌的婆娘弄死，娶我做正房。这样偷偷摸摸的，我已过得腻了！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 583,
      "line_end": 585
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "我那婆娘，岂是那么容易弄死的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 587,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我知道你一定有办法。好人，答应我好么？我一定好好侍候你。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 589,
      "line_end": 591
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你若能套出他的口供，将大旗门藏匿的地方问出来，我就答应你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 593,
      "line_end": 595
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "那还不容易，我这就去……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "慢着！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 599
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "还有什么吩咐？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 601,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "你想要怎样去问他的口供？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 603,
      "line_end": 603
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我现在已将他关在密室刑房里，只要请他尝上几洋刑具的滋味，还怕他不乖乖地说出来么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 607
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "不行不行……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 609,
      "line_end": 609
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "为什么不行？我那么厉害的刑具，纵是铁打的汉子也挺不庄的，何况他一身细皮白肉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 613
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "大旗门的门下弟子，虽不是铁打的身子，却是铁打的心汤，你纵然将他骨头都捏碎，他也不会吐露半个字的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 615,
      "line_end": 617
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "那么……怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 619,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "硬的不行，自然要用软的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 621,
      "line_end": 621
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "你……难道要我用美人计？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 623,
      "line_end": 623
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "除了你那一套之外，世上大概难有人能骗得出他的口风了，只好请你帮帮忙……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 625,
      "line_end": 625
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "你当我是什么人？怎么能对别的男人那样！我跟了你以后，一直死心塌地，你……你却叫我……去……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 627,
      "line_end": 629
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "黛黛，我知道你好，但……这是无可奈何的事，你……你就为我牺牲这一次好么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 631,
      "line_end": 633
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "我知道，我知道……我……我愿意为你牺牲，我愿意为你做任何事……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 639,
      "line_end": 639
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "黛黛，真的，我永远也不会忘了你的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 641,
      "line_end": 641
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "那么，你叫我怎么做呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 643,
      "line_end": 643
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "事成之后，你就可亲手将他杀死！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 645,
      "line_end": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "text": "依你，什么都依你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 649,
      "line_end": 649
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_tu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "司徒笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个装模作样的贱人，你所作所为，还以为我不知道么？只是我对你还没有玩腻，所以一直狠不了心下手杀你而已！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 653,
      "line_end": 655
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "敏儿！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 659,
      "line_end": 661
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_er",
      "speaker_name": "敏儿",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "夫人有什么吩咐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 663,
      "line_end": 663
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "方才那少年……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 665,
      "line_end": 665
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_min_er",
      "speaker_name": "敏儿",
      "listener": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "text": "我已将他送到听雨坞去了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 667,
      "line_end": 667
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dai_dai",
      "speaker_name": "温黛黛",
      "listener": "char_min_er",
      "text": "鬼丫头，只有你猜得出我的心意，等两天一定要你也……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
